market and commodities intelligence and sp dow jones indices indices the ratings segment is an independent provider of credit ratings research and analytics offering investors and other market participants information ratings and benchmarks the market and commodities intelligence segment is a global provider of multiassetclass data research and analytical capabilities which integrate crossasset analytics and desktop services and deliver its customers commodity and energy markets access to highvalue information data analytic services and pricing and quality benchmarks the sp dow jones indices segment is global index provider that maintains a wide variety of valuation and index benchmarks for investment advisors wealth managers and institutional investors the company was founded by james h mcgraw and john a hill in  and is headquartered in new york ny see full profile analyst ratings sell under hold over buy number of ratings  full ratings top picks for the rest of  courtesy of ubs may   at  pm et on benzingacom benzingas top upgrades downgrades for april   apr   at  am et on benzingacom barclays makes sp global a new top pick in info services sector sep   at  am et on benzingacom competitors name chg  market cap thomson reuters corp  b morningstar inc  b factset research systems inc  b john wiley  sons inc cl a  b moodys corp  b competitor data provided by partner content trending tickers powered by amzn  dvax  sbux  bidu  mo  advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found video center learn morestoryful a division of news corp which owns marketwatch is a leading social media services company headquartered in dublin ireland storyful combines world class journalism with industryleading technology to discover verify and acquire original content and provide the ontheground sources news and media organizations need to tell the stories that matter to their audience mcgraw hill financial changes name to sp global inc mcgraw hill financial changes name to sp