 sp global market intelligence and sp global platts and is the majority owner of the sp dow jones indices joint venture contents  corporate history  corporate organization  sp global ratings  sp global market intelligence  sp dow jones indices  sp global platts  presidents of the company  acquisitions  divestitures  books published by mcgrawhill  the mcgrawhill building  connection to the family of george w bush  mcgrawhill federal credit union  awards  references  external links corporate historyedit the predecessor companies of sp global have history dating to  when james h mcgraw purchased the american journal of railway appliances he continued to add further publications eventually establishing the mcgraw publishing company in  john a hill had also produced several technical and trade publications and in  formed his own business the hill publishing company in  both men having known each others interests agreed upon an alliance and combined the book departments of their publishing companies into the mcgrawhill book company john hill served as president with james mcgraw as vicepresident in  the remaining parts of each business were merged into the mcgrawhill publishing company in  mcgrawhill bought out competitor the economy company then the united states largest publisher of educational material the buyout made mcgrawhill the largest educational publisher in the united states in  after hill died merged both mcgrawhill publishing company and mcgrawhill book company into mcgrawhill inc in  mcgrawhill purchased credit rating agency standard  poors in  mcgrawhill purchased byte magazine from its ownerpublisher virginia williamson who then became a vicepresident of mcgrawhill in  mcgrawhill inc became the mcgrawhill companies inc as part of a corporate rebrandingnot in citation given in  mcgrawhill launched an online study network gradegurucom which gave mcgrawhill an opportunity to connect directly with its end users the students the site closed on april   on october   mcgrawhill announced it was selling its entire television station group to the e w scripps company for  million the sale was completed on december   it had been involved in broadcasting since  when it purchased four television stations from a division of time inc mcgraw hill has produced the glencoe series of books for decades on november   mcgrawhill announced it was selling its entire education division known as mcgrawhill education to apollo global management for  billion on march   it announced it had completed the sale for  billion cash on may   shareholders of mcgrawhill voted to change the companys name to mcgraw hill financial mcgrawhill divested the subsidiary mcgrawhill construction to symphony technology group for us million on september   the sale included engineering newsrecord architectural record dodge and sweets mcgrawhill construction has been renamed dodge data  analytics in february  it was announced that mcgrawhill financial would change its name to sp global inc by the end of april  the company officially changed its name following a shareholder vote on april   in april  the company announced it was selling jd power and associates to investment firm xio group for  billion corporate organizationedit sp global now organizes its businesses in four units based on the market in which they are involved sp global ratingsedit sp global ratings provides independent investment research including ratings on various investment instruments sp global market intelligenceedit sp global market intelligence is a provider of multiasset class and realtime data research news and analytics to institutional investors investment and commercial banks investment advisors and wealth managers corporations and universities subsidiaries include leveraged commentary  data sp dow jones indicesedit launched on july   sp dow jones indices is the worlds largest global resource for indexbased concepts data and research it produces the sp  and the dow jones industrial average sp dow jones indices calculates over  indices publishes benchmarks that provide the basis for  etfs globally with  billion in assets invested and serves as the dna for  trillion of the world’s indexed assets sp global plattsedit headquartered in london sp global platts is a provider of information and a source of benchmark price assessments for the commodities energy petrochemicals metals and agriculture markets it has offices in more than  cities including major energy centres such as london dubai singapore and houston and international business centres such as são paulo shanghai and new york city presidents of the companyedit james h mcgraw – johnathan heflin – james mcgraw jr – curtis w mcgraw – donald c mcgraw – shelton fisher – harold mcgraw jr – joseph dionne – harold w mcgraw iii – douglas l peterson –present acquisitionsedit during the course of its history mcgraw hill and from  sp global has expanded significantly through acquisition not just within the publishing industry but also into other areas such as financial services the purchase of standard  poors in  and broadcasting the  acquisition of timelife broadcasting please note that the publishing and education assets are a part of mcgrawhill education from the company separation in  date of acquisition asset acquired industry  newton falls paper company   aw shaw company publisher of magazines and textbooks s gregg company publisher of vocational textbooks  companies of warren c platts including platts publisher of petroleum industry information  fw dodge corporation publisher of construction industry information  california test bureau developer of educational testing systems  standard  poors financial services  shepards citations legal publisher  national radio institute correspondence school  the ryerson press educational and trade publishing  television stations of time life broadcasting broadcasting  the economy company educational publishing  random house schools and colleges educational publishing  times mirror higher education educational publishing  micropal group limited financial services  appleton  lange publisher of medical information  tribune education including ntccontemporary publisher of supplementary educational materials  open university press university press  academic publications  jd power  associates marketing information provider  snl financial financial news note that this list only includes acquisitions made by mcgrawhill not its subsidiaries mcgrawhill typically does not release financial information regarding its acquisitions or divestitures divestituresedit after acquiring a portfolio of diverse companies mcgraw hill later divested itself of many units to form mcgraw hill financial which is now sp global date of divestiture asset relinquished industry  television station group to the e w scripps company broadcasting  mcgrawhill education to apollo global management publishing  mcgrawhill construction to symphony technology group publishing  jd power  associates to xio group marketing information provider note that this list only includes divestitures made by mcgrawhill not its subsidiaries books published by mcgrawhilledit  conference booth see also categorymcgrawhill books mcgrawhill maintained a general publishing division for some years whose best known book was the unpublished autobiography of howard hughes a fake biography of howard hughes by clifford irving which caused a scandal at the time the mcgrawhill buildingedit  avenue of the americas former mcgrawhill headquarters main article  avenue of the americas the company was based at  avenue of the americas otherwise known as the mcgrawhill building until july  the building in new york city has received prominent attention in april  surveillance camera footage was released of nicholas white a production manager for businessweek then published by mcgrawhill who was trapped in the buildings elevator for  hours in october  connection to the family of george w bushedit the mcgraws and the george w bush family have close ties dating back several generations harold mcgraw jr deceased was a member of the national grant advisory and founding board of the barbara bush foundation for family literacy mcgrawhill federal credit unionedit established in  the mcgrawhill federal credit union originally served employees of the mcgrawhill companies in new york city only the credit union moved from its location inside the mcgrawhill building to east windsor new jersey in  its accounts are insured by the national credit union administration it provides savings checking accounts cds moneymarket accounts iras credit cards auto loans and home mortgages awardsedit in  the national building museum presented the mcgrawhill companies with its annual honor award for the corporations contributions to the built environment referencesedit  a b mcgraw hill moves downtown says goodbye to namesake building the wall street journal retrieved  july    a b c d e mcgrawhill cos forbes   a b c news release  mcgraw hill financial investormhficom retrieved    about us corporate history the foundation retrieved may     a b tipton david  mcgraw hill buying the economy company the journal record  accessdate requires url help  about us corporate history the information age retrieved may     nick desantis april   socialstudying network to close chronicle of higher education   mcgrawhill sells tv group to scripps tvnewscheck october     new york times november    the mcgrawhill companies completes sale of mcgrawhill education to apollo press release mcgrawhill companies  march  retrieved  february    staley eddie september   mcgraw hill financial to sell mcgraw hill construction to symphony technology group for m in cash benzinga retrieved april     mcgraw hill sells enr and construction group to equity investor  maidenberg micah december   best year since  for construction industry crains chicago business dodge data  analytics a data provider formerly known as mcgrawhill construction   m